txt.en: Zarkul-sulûn can be found in southern Elderslade.\n\nYou should defeat enemies within the ruins of Zarkul-sulûn.
Zarkul-sulûn is crawling with enemies who need to be removed.
'Laugi told me he asked you to thin the ranks of the enemies in Zarkul-sulûn. Well done, friend. You have done for us a great service this day.'
Gunvald is in Annâk-khurfu in Elderslade.\n\nReturn to Gunvald.
'Well met, friend. The enemy is thick around the ruins of Zarkul-sulûn. Anything you can do to thin their ranks will greatly help the cause.'
